{"tid":729802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[即場被狗屌!] 汲水門大橋8車相撞　入機場嚴重擠塞","createTime":"2018-07-05T01:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T05:21:32.000Z","uid":23707,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f67796bf54e574fe4eaf17bf85e8f32f5aab2e","tid":729802,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:10:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180705/bkn-20180705084904688-0705_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180705%2Fbkn-20180705084904688-0705_00822_001.html&d=rsDJBa8lbVk3udcJb1DQE0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a1638a0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180705/bkn-20180705084904688-0705_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n天雨路滑又無暴雨警告下，汲水門大橋發生8臭花蟹車相撞意外。今(5日)早8時許，青衣汲水門大橋往機場方向，有8輛由盲人或痙攣人士駕駛的私家車疑因天雨下在大直路發生碰撞，橫亘在行車線上，警方接報到場調查，屌你老味，受本來可避免的意外影響，現場交通嚴撚柒重受阻，入機場方向車龍延至汀九橋及長青隧道口，預計8個司機好快被狗屌死。"},{"pid":"b98578a44b59c22b46c9200700af44b41b26db58","tid":729802,"uid":17167,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b3f67796bf54e574fe4eaf17bf85e8f32f5aab2e","tid":729802,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:10:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180705/bkn-20180705084904688-0705_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180705%2Fbkn-20180705084904688-0705_00822_001.html&d=rsDJBa8lbVk3udcJb1DQE0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a1638a0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180705/bkn-20180705084904688-0705_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n天雨路滑又無暴雨警告下，汲水門大橋發生8臭花蟹車相撞意外。今(5日)早8時許，青衣汲水門大橋往機場方向，有8輛由盲人或痙攣人士駕駛的私家車疑因天雨下在大直路發生碰撞，橫亘在行車線上，警方接報到場調查，屌你老味，受本來可避免的意外影響，現場交通嚴撚柒重受阻，入機場方向車龍延至汀九橋及長青隧道口，預計8個司機好快被狗屌死。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj